  "text": "Ler, Tir, and EspA were analyzed by Western blotting as described [CITATION_1] . Proteins were electroblotted onto a PVDF membrane and probed with either mouse DnaK mAb (1:10,000; Enzo), Ler pAb (1:2,500; provided by I. Rosenshine), EspA pAb (1:50,000; provided by J. Kaper), or Tir pAb (1:50,000; provided by J. Kaper). Experiments were repeated at least three times.",
